         <abstract id="aspace_8e5a3404ddbe94e716dc7e843c34cf0d">The Radical Sex and Leather Collection includes assorted illustrated publications and ephemera, generally produced by the radical sex and leather communities, documenting the development of a wide array of sexual practices, costumes, and communities.</abstract>
    
