      <scopecontent id="aspace_2781b43cc31e83731473643ab080b42c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Radical Sex and Leather Collection includes assorted illustrated publications and ephemera, generally produced by the radical sex and leather communities, documenting the development of a wide array of sexual practices, costumes, and communities.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
